+### 3.5 Critic Feedback жөјзҠ»вӮ¬жҺ‘еҙ—з’Ғ?+
+`CriticAgent` йҗЁеӢ¬жҹҠйҺәгғҘеҪӣжқ©ж–ҝжҙ– `CritiqueResult`й”ӣеұјз¬үйҚҗе¶…еҪ§йҸ„?`list[ReviewIssue]`й”ӣ?+
+```python
+# models.py йҸӮжқҝо–ғ
+@dataclass(slots=True)
+class UncertainFeedbackItem:
+    issue_id: str
+    category: str
+    critic_reason: str   # e.g. "evidence E-003 еҜ®жӣ ж•ӨйҗЁеӢ®о”‘йҚҷ?42 з“’е‘ӯеҡӯ changed entity й‘јеҶЁжҙҝ 10-35"
+    original_confidence: float
+
+@dataclass(slots=True)
+class PriorFeedback:
+    iteration: int
